19981120183900000_1	Sex at a molecular level is spawning an elite class of proteins.	sex molecular level spawn elit class protein
19981120183900000_2	has used a DNA shuffling technique to create interferons that are dramatically more effective against viruses than any produced naturally by the immune system.	ha use dna shuffl techniqu creat interferon dramat effect virus ani produc natur immun system
19981120183900000_3	It has also made ultra efficient versions of an industrial enzyme.	ha also made ultra effici version industri enzym
19981120183900000_4	When organisms reproduce sexually the offspring end up with a mix and match set of genes inherited from both parents.	organ reproduc sexual offspr end mix match set gene inherit parent
19981120183900000_5	Maxygen s technique is similar except the parents are a series of related genes.	maxygen techniqu similar except parent seri relat gene
19981120183900000_6	These are cut into pieces shuffled together and then assembled to form a new genetic generation.	cut piec shuffl togeth assembl form new genet gener
19981120183900000_7	Some of these daughter genes can manufacture proteins that are much better at certain tasks than nature s originals.	daughter gene manufactur protein much better certain task natur origin
19981120183900000_8	The best ones can be screened out and shuffled to produce whole lineages of superior descendants in a process mimicking evolution by natural selection.	best one screen shuffl produc whole lineag superior descend process mimick evolut natur select
19981120183900000_9	Maxygen s technique was described earlier this year in Nature (vol.	maxygen techniqu wa describ earlier thi year natur vol
19981120183900000_10	The parent genes are first broken into fragments by shattering their DNA with ultrasound or cutting them up with an enzyme called DNAse.	parent gene first broken fragment shatter dna ultrasound cut enzym call dna se
19981120183900000_11	They are reassembled into daughter genes comprising fragments from several parents using a variant of the DNA building polymerase chain reaction.	reassembl daughter gene compris fragment sever parent use variant dna build polymeras chain reaction
19981120183900000_12	Short template or primer sequences ensure that the fragments are stitched together in the correct order to produce a functioning gene.	short templat primer sequenc ensur fragment stitch togeth correct order produc function gene
19981120183900000_13	The daughter genes can then be inserted into bacteria or fungi where they begin making protein.	daughter gene insert bacteria fungi begin make protein
19981120183900000_14	To make superior versions of an industrial enzyme the identity of which is still secret Maxygen s scientists isolated genes from 26 microorganisms which each make their own versions of the enzyme.	make superior version industri enzym ident still secret maxygen scientist isol gene microorgan make version enzym
19981120183900000_15	Using its system of DNA shuffling Maxygen made 600 new daughter genes 77 of which produced superior enzymes.	use system dna shuffl maxygen made new daughter gene produc superior enzym
19981120183900000_16	Screening showed up variants which functioned better than natural enzymes at high low or intermediate pH.	screen show variant function better natur enzym high low intermedi ph
19981120183900000_17	They re all highly significant commercially says Pim Stemmer Maxygen s vice president of research.	highli signific commerci say pim stemmer maxygen vice presid research
19981120183900000_18	Maxygen has also shuffled genes that make the 20 known human interferons.	maxygen ha also shuffl gene make known human interferon
19981120183900000_19	This time they made 2 000 daughter genes and once again the results were spectacular.	thi time made daughter gene onc result spectacular
19981120183900000_20	The best interferon produced by the genes was 285 000 times as potent as interferon alpha 2b which is marketed as a drug as measured by its ability to protect cultured cells against a mouse virus.	best interferon produc gene wa time potent interferon alpha b market drug measur abil protect cultur cell mous viru
19981120183900000_21	It could prove a major moneyspinner for Maxygen.	could prove jor money spinner maxygen
19981120183900000_22	Sales of interferon alpha 2b which is used to treat viral diseases and cancer pull in 600 million each year for Schering Plough of Berlin.	sale interferon alpha b use treat viral diseas cancer pull million year schere plough berlin
